query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('aws-lambda',
'compiler-errors',
'ecmascript-6',
'exception-handling',
'for-loop',
'html5',
'jsf',
'memory',
'optimization',
'set',
'type-conversion');
